A '''munjandie''' is an obsolete unit of mass in [[India]] approximately equal to 4&nbsp;grains (0.259&nbsp;g).<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sizes.com/units/munjandie.htm |title=Munjandie|website=Sizes: The Online Quantinary|accessdate=2018-09-15}}</ref> After [[Metrication in India|metrication]] in the mid-20th century, the unit became obsolete.
